trans-unit.source: Represents a type of a SharePoint project item.
trans-unit.target: 表示 SharePoint 项目项的类型。

trans-unit.source: It enables users to associate custom data with a type because it inherits from the <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.IAnnotatedObject" /> interface.
trans-unit.target: 它使用户能够将自定义数据与类型关联，因为它继承自 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.IAnnotatedObject" /> 接口。

trans-unit.source: Gets the unique ID of the SharePoint project item type.
trans-unit.target: 获取 SharePoint 项目项类型的唯一 ID。

trans-unit.source: A string representing an ID.
trans-unit.target: 一个字符串，表示一个 id。

trans-unit.source: The ID is usually a string which appears as a namespace qualified type.
trans-unit.target: 该 ID 通常是一个字符串，它显示为命名空间限定类型。

trans-unit.source: The ID is initialized by the project from the SharePointProjectItemTypeAttribute.<xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.SharePointProjectItemTypeAttribute.ProjectItemTypeId%2A> value provided for the <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectItemTypeProvider> component.
trans-unit.target: 通过从 SharePointProjectItemTypeAttribute 项目初始化 ID。<xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.SharePointProjectItemTypeAttribute.ProjectItemTypeId%2A>为提供值<xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectItemTypeProvider>组件。

trans-unit.source: The ID must match the ID stored in the .SPData file.
trans-unit.target: ID 必须匹配中存储的 ID。SPData 文件。

trans-unit.source: Gets whether the project item is valid.
trans-unit.target: 了解项目项是否有效。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="True" /> if the project item is valid; <see langword="false" /> otherwise.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="True" /> 如果项目项是有效，则为<see langword="false" />否则为。

trans-unit.source: A project item type is considered to be valid if the SharePoint project can find a component implementing the corresponding project item type provider, and if the provider was able to successfully create and initialize the type.
trans-unit.target: 项目项类型被视为如果 SharePoint 项目可以找到组件实现相应项目项类型提供程序，并且能够成功创建并初始化此类型提供程序是否可有效。

trans-unit.source: Gets the friendly name of type shown in designers.
trans-unit.target: 获取设计器中显示类型的友好名称。

trans-unit.source: By default, the name is the ID.
trans-unit.target: 默认情况下，名称为 ID。

trans-unit.source: A string representing a type name.
trans-unit.target: 表示类型名称的字符串。

trans-unit.source: Gets an instance of the SharePoint project service.
trans-unit.target: 获取 SharePoint 项目服务的实例。

trans-unit.source: An object representing a SharePoint project service instance.
trans-unit.target: 表示一个 SharePoint 项目服务实例的对象。

trans-unit.source: Gets the deployment location of the assembly that is supported by this <see cref="P:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectItemFile.ProjectItem" />.
trans-unit.target: 获取此 <see cref="P:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectItemFile.ProjectItem" /> 支持的程序集的部署位置。

trans-unit.source: An object representing a deployment location.
trans-unit.target: 表示一个部署位置的对象。

trans-unit.source: Gets the scope at which the deployment of the <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectItem" /> is supported in SharePoint.
trans-unit.target: 获取 SharePoint 中支持 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectItem" /> 部署的范围。

trans-unit.source: An object representing a deployment scope.
trans-unit.target: 表示部署范围的对象。

trans-unit.source: This property used in selecting a compatible feature for auto-add and restricting the feature and package designer UIs, among other uses.
trans-unit.target: 在选择包括为兼容的功能和限制功能和包设计器用户界面，对于其他用户使用此属性。

trans-unit.source: Gets the trust levels in SharePoint supported by the <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectItem" />.
trans-unit.target: 获取 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectItem" /> 支持的 SharePoint 中的信任级别。

trans-unit.source: An object representing trust levels.
trans-unit.target: 表示信任级别的对象。
